                     <interp inst="t18030914-7-off42" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030914-7-off42" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18030914-7-cd43" type="crimeDate">13th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030914-7-off42 t18030914-7-cd43"></join>, a<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="180309140006"></xptr>pair of stockings, value 5s. 6d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18030914-7-victim113" type="victimName">
